flowchart LR
  A[(User Input\nBrief, constraints, preferences)]
  --> B[Research Agent\nRowan]
  B --> C[Strategy Brief\n(Rowan output)]
  C --> D[Creative Director\nZara]
  D --> E[Director Handoff\n(brief + constraints)]
  E --> F[Designer Executor\n(1 profile: logo | typography | packaging)]
  F --> G[Draft Deliverables\nLogo, type, color, layout]
  G --> H[Deterministic Validators\nTypography + layout + brand checks]
  H --> I{Director Gate\nLOOP_POLICY.json}
  I -->|REVISE| B
  I -->|SHIP| J[SHIP Pack\nlabel.png, brand-board.png, product-mock.png, manifest.json]
  I -->|STOP| K[Loop Ends\nmax review hit]
  J --> L[Handoff\n/send to self-learning + QA]
  D --> M[No-feedback mode\noptional autonomous run]
